videos.description: Kentucky quarterback Terry Wilson takes off down the middle for a huge 42-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Kentucky QB runs for 42-yard TD

videos.description: Benny Snell smashes his way through the Murray State defense for his 35th career score to put Kentucky up 17-0.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell powers his way to a TD

videos.description: Murray State's DeQuan Dallas can't bring down the pass as he's involved in a huge collision with a Kentucky defender. Both players would be fine after the play.
videos.headline: Big collision leads to incomplete pass for Murray State

videos.description: Asim Rose increases Kentucky's lead over Murray State with a 3-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Rose runs 3 yards for the TD

videos.description: Kentucky runs a double reverse, leading to a Zy'Aire Hughes 49 -yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Trick play leads to a 49-yard TD run for Kentucky

videos.description: Gunnar Hoak fights through multiple defenders and a face mask penalty to pick up the 23-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Hoak fights his way 23 yards for TD

videos.description: Kentucky's red shirt freshman Danny Clark gets his first touchdown of the game to put the Wildcats  up 48-3.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Clark runs for 2-yard TD
